29
00:01:18,286 --> 00:01:21,539
‎伙计们 这礼物我喜欢
‎你们怎么知道我的尺码的？
Guys, I love it. How did you know my size?

30
00:01:22,248 --> 00:01:25,085
‎我们给你买了超大号
‎好让大家一起享用
We got you an extra large
so we can enjoy it too.

31
00:01:26,753 --> 00:01:28,296
‎这椅子是不是太小了？
Is this chair too small?

32
00:01:29,672 --> 00:01:31,758
‎赶紧把生日卡给莉亚啊
Just give Leia our birthday card already.

33
00:01:32,258 --> 00:01:33,176
‎里猫猫
Inside cat.

34
00:01:33,259 --> 00:01:34,928
‎外猫猫
[gasps] Outside cat.

35
00:01:35,011 --> 00:01:37,764
‎里猫猫 外猫猫 里…
Inside cat. Outside cat. Ins--

36
00:01:37,847 --> 00:01:38,681
‎别猫猫了
No more cat.

37
00:01:39,224 --> 00:01:42,644
‎我好想你们
‎没有你们 我的伤心洞好寂寞
I missed you guys.
My sad hole was lonely without you.

38
00:01:43,728 --> 00:01:46,856
‎我不会让分手毁了我的生日
I'm not gonna let my breakup with Jay
ruin my birthday.

39
00:01:46,940 --> 00:01:48,108
‎这不叫分手
Not a breakup.

40
00:01:49,192 --> 00:01:50,193
‎这不叫分手
Not a breakup.

41
00:01:51,194 --> 00:01:52,403
‎-不叫分手
‎-不叫分手？
[both] Not a breakup.

42
00:01:53,321 --> 00:01:55,824
‎人生中能有几回十五岁？
How many times
do you turn 15 in your life?

43
00:01:56,366 --> 00:01:57,367
‎没几回
Not that many.

44
00:01:58,827 --> 00:01:59,911
