Nik!

53
00:02:17,595 --> 00:02:19,764
‎要走了吗？我才刚调好
People are leaving? I just got this right.

54
00:02:19,848 --> 00:02:21,683
‎一 二 三 四
-[rock music playing]
<i>-One, two, three, four!</i>

55
00:02:21,766 --> 00:02:23,768
‎在街上闲逛
<i>♪ Hangin' out down the street ♪</i>

56
00:02:23,852 --> 00:02:25,728
‎和上周没什么两样
<i>♪ The same old thing we did last week ♪</i>

57
00:02:25,812 --> 00:02:27,939
‎没什么事好做 就跟你唠唠嗑
<i>♪ Not a thing to do ♪</i>

58
00:02:28,022 --> 00:02:30,024
‎没什么事好做 就跟你唠唠嗑
<i>♪ But talk to you ♪</i>

59
00:02:30,108 --> 00:02:31,401
‎这样挺好 这样挺好
<i>♪ We're all all right! ♪</i>

60
00:02:31,484 --> 00:02:32,735
‎这样挺好 这样挺好
<i>♪ We're all all right! ♪</i>

61
00:02:33,319 --> 00:02:35,363
