-You did one thing. Good for you.
-[egg cracks]

78
00:03:32,295 --> 00:03:35,173
‎抱歉 我发脾气了 就…过生日真好玩
I'm sorry. I snapped.
It's… Birthdays are fun.

79
00:03:35,256 --> 00:03:36,674
[laughs]

80
00:03:36,758 --> 00:03:38,718
‎今天会很漫长
It's gonna be a long day.

81
00:03:39,761 --> 00:03:42,263
‎哈啰 哈啰 哈啰啰
Hey there! Hi there! Ho there!

82
00:03:43,806 --> 00:03:45,934
